# AI Interview - Cursor Rules

## PROJE KIMLIGI

Bu proje **AI Interview** - yapay zeka destekli gercek zamanli sesli gorusme sistemidir.

**Tech Stack:**
- Frontend: Next.js 15 (App Router), TailwindCSS, shadcn/ui, Zustand
- Backend: Node.js + Express.js, PostgreSQL
- AI Services: Claude Sonnet 4.5, OpenAI Whisper (STT), ElevenLabs Turbo (TTS), Simli (Avatar)
- Realtime: WebSocket (ws package)
- Package Manager: pnpm (monorepo)

**Durum:** Phase 1-6 tamamlandi. Sistem calisiyor. Yeni ozellikler `docs/features/` altindan planlanir.

---

